title: Week 8 Waivers 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp recap MNF, give injury updates, react to a key trade and talk what players are trending up for the rest of the season. Plus, Eric Moody joins the show to discuss the players you have to add for Week 8.
